      *                      * de                                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        srt-tip-fnz          not  = 01  and
                     srt-tip-fnz          not  = 04  and
                     srt-tip-fnz          not  = 06  and
                     srt-tip-fnz          not  = 07
                     go to prn-liv-det-600.
