           add       1                    to   w-cgs-wrk-pos          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Descrizione sottogruppo                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      w-cgs-wrk-car        to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
